<Paragraph>
Microsoft Office Excel 2007 provides tables support that makes managing and analyzing data with ease and efficient. These tables come with specific style support.
</Paragraph>
<Paragraph>
XlsIO supports reading and writing tables in Excel 2007 format. Tables can be created from any input range of sheet data and the total row can be inserted into the table. Styles can also be applied to the tables.
</Paragraph>

